errors
one faulty sensor (shows there is a car when there is not, should eventually (10 rounds) turn the lights yellow)
visuality of this fault is shown with observation of the one faulty sensor
in addition a Q test and T^2 test will be made

for simplicity's sake the faulty sensor will be the sensor 1

